title: UPS Synchronization Failure
content: During load testing, the Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) systems failed to synchronize with the backup generators, leading to unstable voltage output.
resolutionMethod: Reprogram the synchronization logic controller and recalibrate the UPS communication parameters.

title: Cooling Unit Underperformance
content: One of the CRAC (Computer Room Air Conditioning) units is underperforming, maintaining 3C above the target setpoint.
resolutionMethod:
Check refrigerant levels, inspect compressor operation, and verify airflow control actuators.
Finished
